{"tid":2513494,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［似曾相識的畫面］曼聯反格拉沙會示威","createTime":"2021-05-02T14:20:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T14:31:40.000Z","uid":80564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5cd6517ae5d7d3d120235d5105701ff921a8fe59","tid":2513494,"uid":80564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T14:20:51.000Z","msg":"話咁快已經見到兩黨派：<br />\n支持示威黨：「好呀反格拉沙，最好場場都踢唔成！」<br />\n<br />\n反對示威黨：「你地表達意見還表達，可唔可以唔好阻我睇波呀？好擾民呀！」<br />\n<br />\n呢啲對白，係咪好似曾相識呢？<br />\n格拉沙會同你講：「道歉我就做咗，想我走呢就無可能，你地繼續攬炒啦。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZY12z43B8jK9PEMZN452o1pYxCs5BnU1LXfaeEFLUGKA?filename=ZDnYRWt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZDnYRWt.jpg&h=9ceee7f4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"192d476d24e57dee417fa225478491ba04e4a259","tid":2513494,"uid":80564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T14:23:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ae8516675518648849dc57d52bcdf0f395984e","tid":2513494,"uid":80564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T14:28:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f606b2e197e9425a8145c4990b0480bb8c7343ae","tid":2513494,"uid":80564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T14:31:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}